<%- include("partials-header") %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">Prototype System Flow</h2>

  <div class="card shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-body p-4">
      <div class="flow-step">
        <span>1</span>
        <div>
          <h5>Merchant creates payment request</h5>
          <p>Merchant enters SGD amount, preferred crypto, and network.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-step">
        <span>2</span>
        <div>
          <h5>Uniweb generates payment page</h5>
          <p>The app calculates mock crypto amount and creates a mock BVNK wallet address.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-step">
        <span>3</span>
        <div>
          <h5>Customer pays crypto</h5>
          <p>In the prototype, this is simulated using a button instead of a real blockchain transfer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-step">
        <span>4</span>
        <div>
          <h5>Mock BVNK confirms payment</h5>
          <p>The system changes payment status from PENDING to PAID.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-step">
        <span>5</span>
        <div>
          <h5>Mock SGD settlement</h5>
          <p>The system simulates BVNK converting the crypto/stablecoin and settling SGD to the merchant.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
    <strong>Prototype Boundary:</strong> Real crypto transfer, blockchain monitoring, BVNK API calls, bank settlement, and compliance checks are outside the prototype scope.
  </div>
</div>

<%- include("partials-footer") %>
